Section 1 - Header
    -You need a website. We can do it for you. We design and develop professional, responsive websites and maintain them for you to save you time. 

Section 2 - About us
    -SpiderWebs is web development company that aims to deliver only the best professional web services. We offer professional and affordable web services for any kind of business or individual. With us, not only do you get a domain and web host included in any package you pick, but you also get monthly maintainance included. Saving you gang time you would've spent digging into all that technicall stuff. Whether you a business or an individual, you need a website to effectively commincate your brand and project the brand's image. SpyderWebs can take care of that for you.

Section 3 - Services
    -We design, develop and maintain your website. All our packages include a domain name, web host and monthly web maintainance.

    Responsive
    Our websites are optimized for all screen sizes. With technology changing and improving so rapidly, it is critical for you website to be accessible via all devices, regardless of their screen size.

    User Friendly
    Making your website user friendly is one the aspects we focus on most. Having a website that not user friendly can very easily drive away potential customers. Our websites are easy to use and easy to navigate through them.

    Monthly Maintainance
    On a monthly basis we scan your website for any security faults, bugs and errors, and terminate any we find. We will also update the site where necessary. You will be contacted in advance before the monthly maintainance to discuss what you want changed and updated.

    Monthly reporting
    You will receive a full statistics report on a monthly basis. With this report, you will see detailed stats e.g. visitors, page hits, time spent on page etc, with demographics of each stat e.g. Location, device, time etc.

   Process
   You can contact us through the contact form below. Once we receive your request, we'll contact you back via E-mail to discyss 

